nouns

1.  Player class : -help in initializing a game player(player name)
    -contains user 1/0
    -contains player lives (3 by default)
    variable : @name @life
    methods : remove_a_life,

2.  question class : class inherited by each question.
    takes in a user answer and checks if question[:answer] === user_answer

        variables: @answer

    methods : generate_question, check_answer?

3.  game class : contains current_player and game loop
    -keeps track of player scores (so, it should probably have access to player_lives)
    variables: @current_player
    method : start_game, game_over, game_winner, next_turn(updates current_player)
